<p>The <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">eth0</code> entry shows the IP address assigned by the Mac to the BBG was <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">169.254.120.60</code>.
From another terminal window on your Mac, you should be able to log into the BBG:</p>
<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>phwl@PHWL-MBP ~ % ssh debian@169.254.120.60
